                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>An article entitled “Is War with Russia Inevitable? Five Solid Arguments for
                    Peace,” written by the Counselor of the Department <pb facs="1124" n="1108"
                        xml:id="pg_1108"/> of State, George F. Kennan, was printed in the <hi
                        rend="italic">Reader’s Digest</hi> for March 1950, and has been reprinted in
                    the Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, February 20, 1950,
                    pages 267–271, 303.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
